\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>These days, the problem is a thing of the past, but the folk art of Zalipie has become part of the village&#x2019;s identity, a tradition that they are very proud of. Even in war-time, the flower painting continued, giving the village hope and color in dark times.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tour-zalipie-village\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your tour to Zalipie easily online.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/45247&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105919\/zalipie-poland-most-beautiful-village-scaled.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.salti