uses-zalipie-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110012\/beautiful-painted-houses-zalipie.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">The Zalipie Experience<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To encourage these traditions to continue, every year, the Ethnographic museum of Tarnow organizes a cottage painting competition. Every June, the locals of Zalipie enter their decorated homes into the competition. Cash prizes are awarded for originality and artistic flair, often with many generations competing together. The competition is a beautiful way to maintain the tradition of folk art in Zalipie, as each person taking part brings a fresh take on the typical folk art.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/krakow\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">12 Things to do in Krakow, Poland<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do poland Zalipie painted village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do poland Zalipie painted village\" class=\"wp-image-46483 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110000\/best-things-to-do-poland-Zalipie-painted-village-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2311000