held here. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Opening Times:<\/strong> October 01-May 31 from 8 AM-4 PM. In the summer months, the museum is open from Mon-Fri 8 AM-4 PM and at the weekends 11 AM-4 PM.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105944\/Zalipie-Painted-Village-Poland-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Zalipie Painted Village Poland\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Zalipie Painted Village Poland\" data-id=\"46489\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105944\/Zalipie-Painted-Village-Poland.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=46489\" class=\"wp-image-46489 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105944\/Zalipie-Painted-Village-Poland-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105944\/Zalipie-Painted-Village-Poland-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105944\/Zalipie-Painted-Village-Poland-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23105944\/Zalipie-Painted-Village-Poland-400x600.jpg 400w, 