cularly famous and respected for her work. She kept the tradition alive for many years, and her cottage is a perfect example. The house has been preserved as it was when she lived there for tourists to visit with detailed paintings everywhere, even the oven is decorated with typical paintings!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tour-zalipie-village\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your tour to Zalipie easily online.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110005\/beautiful-village-poland-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"beautiful village poland\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"beautiful village poland\" data-id=\"46482\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110005\/beautiful-village-poland.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=46482\" class=\"wp-image-46482 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110005\/beautiful-village-poland-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/23110005\/beautiful-village-poland-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2311