\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-public-transport\">Public Transport<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Unfortunately, there are no direct buses or trains to Zalipie. It is possible to travel from Krakow to Tarnow&#x2019;s city by train or bus (both taking approx 1.5 hours). From Tarnow to Zalipie, you will have to take a 40-minute taxi ride. We highly recommend <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tour-zalipie-village\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">a tour<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-poland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">renting a car<\/a> instead. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"hotels\">Where to Stay in Zalipie<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Because it&#x2019;s a small village, there aren&#x2019;t very many accommodation options in Zalipie. Your best option is to either stay in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/krakow\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Krakow<\/a> or Tarow and travel to Zalipie for the day or as a stopover on your road trip.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>See all:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/krakow-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hotels in Krakow<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"The Story of Zalipie Painted Village Over a hundred years ago in Zalipie, every house had a wood stove but no chimney. Thus,